# Goblin Movie Club Managment App

## Description

The Movie Club Management App is a comprehensive solution designed to streamline the management of movie club operations. Built with the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express.js, React, and Node.js), this app offers a user-friendly interface that enables club administrators to manage members, promote upcoming events, and handle memberships seamlessly. 

With integration of the TMDB API for movie details and Stripe for payment processing, it provides an easy to use interactive experience for both administrators and members. 

## Table of Contents

- [Features](#features)
- [Installation](#installation)
